headline: Evercore downgrades Kraft Heinz on sales headwinds, gross margin risks
summary: Evercore ISI cut its rating on Kraft Heinz (NASDAQ:KHC) stock from Outperform to In-Line and reduced the price target to $35 from the previous $38.
